casebody.data:
No. 65,

Orig.

Texas v. New Mexico. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 506 U. S. 983.]

Motion of the River Master for award of compensation and fees granted, and the River Master is awarded a total of $7,318.93 for the period October 1 through December 31, 1992, to be paid equally by the parties.
